{"ID":"20260305082130-3m0qivo","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3m0qivo","title":"函数模板","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-8gjgshy","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-8gjgshy"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 函数模板\ndate created: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 11:33:18 中午\ndate modified: 星期二, 十一月 4日 2025, 2:37:30 下午\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-epdh4gy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-epdh4gy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 函数模版的定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-y87f4bm","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-y87f4bm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"template \u003cclass T1, typename T2, ...\u003e\nreturnType functionName (T1 a, T2 b, ...)\n{\n\t\\\\ ...\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-y2uhybo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-y2uhybo","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"\u0026lt;模板形参表\u0026gt;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中包含一个或多个用逗号分开的参数项，每一参数至少应在类的说明中出现一次；"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模版的形式参数类型可以使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"class"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 或 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"typename"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（在大多数情况下，两者完全等价，可以互换使用，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"typename"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 更明确地表示这是一个类型参数）以及编译时常量（整型、枚举、指针或引用类型），甚至以模版为参数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-fqtbeia","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fqtbeia","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"例如"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-vi0uov9","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vi0uov9","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 模版\ntemplate \u003cclass T\u003e\nT add(T a, Tb) {\n\tT x;\n\tx = a + b;\n\treturn x;\n}\n\n// 调用时\nint x, y, z;\nx = add(y, z);\n\ndouble x, y, z;\nx = add(y, z);\n\nMAT x, y, z;\nx = add(y, z);\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-qmzob9f","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qmzob9f","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 模版函数的调用"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-gzr2hi5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gzr2hi5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"template int add\u003cint\u003e(int, int); // 强制显式实例化（强制编译器编译该类型的模版函数）\n\nz = add(x, y); // 隐式自动（编译器检测到该调用自动隐式编译该类型的模版函数）\nz = add\u003cint\u003e(x, y); // 强制调用指定类型的函数\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-qpj7wa8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qpj7wa8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ahzeqb7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ahzeqb7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-gi4v24j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gi4v24j","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模板实例函数和函数模板的作用域相同；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-bjdzr5w","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-bjdzr5w","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-2es6uij","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2es6uij","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在调用函数时可隐式自动生成模板实例函数；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-cd9iddh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cd9iddh","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-quu7u9g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-quu7u9g","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"调用时可以指定参数类型，实参按参数类型进行转换。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dlrtpj0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dlrtpj0","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-hpe4oy3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hpe4oy3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可强制显式生成模板实例函数（不调用也生成实例函数）；"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ubdtop9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ubdtop9","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 任意个类型形参的函数模板"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-k1te3u0","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-k1te3u0","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int println() {  \n\tcout \u003c\u003c endl; return 0;  \n} // 手动定义无参的函数\ntemplate \u003c class H,class ...T\u003e // 用…表示任意个类型形参 // 使用模版自动定义 \nint println(H h, T ...t) { //递归下降展开函数的参数表  \n\tcout \u003c\u003c h \u003c\u003c \" * \";  \n\treturn 1 + println(t...); //递归下降调用  \n}  \nint main() { println(1, ‘2’, 3.3, “expand”); }\n//输出 1 * 2 * 3.3 * expand *\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-8gvpjga","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8gvpjga","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4 特化实例函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ah1hkfg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ah1hkfg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"template \u003ctypename T\u003e T max(T a, T b) {  \n\treturn a\u003eb?a:b;  \n}  \ntemplate \u003c \u003e //此行可省，特化实例函数  \nconst char *max(const char *x, const char *y) {  \n\treturn strcmp(x, y)\u003e0?x:y;  \n}  \n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-e3z5m00","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-e3z5m00","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特化实例函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"允许手动定义某个类型的函数，会被优先调用，可用于隐藏模板实例函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-wkyb4gi","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wkyb4gi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-0c977ch","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-0c977ch","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-dihxyvm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dihxyvm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"优先使用实参与形参完全匹配的特化函数；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-xfid5b6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xfid5b6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-sr7vmim","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sr7vmim","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其次使用实参与形参能够匹配的模板实例函数；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-mnu6qfv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mnu6qfv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-k0yoelb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-k0yoelb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明确了实参类型时，对调用实参进行强制类型转换。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-h54ezdh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-h54ezdh","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5 函数模版的特点"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ou3pudg","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ou3pudg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-rtx7hdc","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-rtx7hdc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-6shvi4e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6shvi4e","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数模板只是一种说明，并不是一个具体函数；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-gfifqnw","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gfifqnw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-8o2ltug","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8o2ltug","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译系统对函数模板不产生任何执行代码；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1dn82rq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1dn82rq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vd2leax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vd2leax","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在遇到具体函数调用的时候，根据调用处的具体参数类型，在参数实例化以后才产生相应的代码，此代码称为模板函数。"}]}]}]}]}